Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nkeep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've not seen each other\Nfor a long time. It's Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you see the legendary great\Nmaneuver that I did with Sora?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet everything on that show. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both my own fate and my\Nbond with my best partner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can no longer appear on\NKaleido Stage, but I have no regrets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I found a new dream. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora, follow me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:01:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa \Naka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in U hikikae ni subete ushinatte mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, we've got a vacation! A whole week too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to regular maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take this chance to really\Nmake the rounds of the comedy theatres!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll plan new productions\Nlike crazy at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to spend day and\Nnight on special trapeze training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, would you mind joining me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's so motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be Mina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:02:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I stay like this, I can\Nnever be a real Kaleido Star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. It's nothing. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, when you've changed your clothes,\Ngo to the Boss's office right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a surprise for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow... I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a conditioned reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember there was that time\Nyou had to work during your time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, you should go there\Nexpecting the worst case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shock will be less that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make a guest\Nappearance on stage with Miss Layla?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Layla's recommended you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't like it, do you\Nwant to me to decline the offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the North Pole,\Nthe South Pole, anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora's going to appear\Non stage with Miss Layla?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to see Miss Layla. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Ever Amazing Miss Layla."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Please take me to off-Broadway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, hasn't it, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte... Julie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're working as Miss Layla's\Npersonal assistants now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you, like, haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sora Naegino from Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the producer, Mike Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working\Nwith you for the next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working\Nunder your supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the writer and the\Ndirector of this show, Cathy Taymor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't need to alter costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla fired the previous performer, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a professional\Nperformer with a decent career,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems Layla didn't like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the season, without\Nconsulting the producer or the director!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the kind of thing people normally do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Normally they don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to appear on stage\Nwith someone who doesn't have any zeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I don't like spoiled rich girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her schedule happened\Nto be open, so we're okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what were you going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--if we couldn't find a replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh... well... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't be away\Nfrom Kaleido Stage for more than a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll figure the rest out, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only going to appear in one scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a very important scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scene is Salome's dance,\Nwhich will be in the latter half of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anger and sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love and hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of Salome's passion\Nis poured into that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to fire up the scene with an acrobatic\Nperformance as a shadow of my character,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and raise the temperature of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the temperature of the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've set up the\Nrough outline of how it will go,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how you want to perform is all up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, do it ad lib.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ad lib?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run through the basic outline.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm May Wong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was inspired by you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and joined Kaleido Stage this year \Nwith the top score for new entrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the newcomer who's playing\Nthe leading role in the new production.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm more talented than Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of Sora, please \Nlet me be in the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rolling Flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May found out that I was \Ninvited by Miss Layla{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and came to New York planning to do this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining Flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, May! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who was invited by Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off this stage right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla invited you\Nbecause she didn't know about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, "A super powerful \Nnewcomer appears."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, like, doesn't seem like she can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we put them both on, Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were my thoughts exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's start rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I want to put in an\Nemergency order for another costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think maybe I want one more\Nidea in there to make it fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's put that in tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to the hotel, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I booked a room at the\NCentury Hotel, which is close to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tell me that you're going\Nto put me in the same room with Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}refuse{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, don't be so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather sleep outside\Nthan stay in a room with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! Who wants to\Nbe with someone like you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save that energy for tomorrow's show!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, if the two of you don't mind, why not cancel\Nyour hotel reservation and come to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's New York for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to make coffee now.\NSo make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Try to make"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, that's where you put the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the coffee beans should be ground first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:12:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seldom drink coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having you really helps me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm honored to be of use to you, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla's already \Nstarted her new life here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess the legendary great\Nmaneuver is already part of her past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we put them both on, Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were my thoughts exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not the only one she has hopes for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you quit moping already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moping?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know both\Nof us will be in the show,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't pull yourself together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla will be the one who's embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had so many things I wanted to talk with\NMiss Layla about. I haven't seen her for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, because of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla isn't yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want to talk with Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my dream to\Nappear on the stage with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:13:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to have Miss Layla\Nrecognize me as better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who injured Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone I {\i1}won't {\i0}lose to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say that Sora injured me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't paired with Sora to\Nperform the legendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you never would have been injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt myself because my mind\Nwasn't fully where it needed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still ventured to do the\Nlegendary great maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it meant smashing my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it of my own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's wrong to put the \Nblame on Sora for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer do that kind of performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to my injuries,\NI think I have new opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you hadn't injured your shoulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right now you would be in\Nan even larger-scale show...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I chose that show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I performed the \Nlegendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when people heard that I would\Nnot go back to Kaleido Stage anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a lot of job offers to be\Nin movies, plays, and TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, after having accomplished\Nthe legendary great maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,none of them appealed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. A script.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's the injury? When will it be healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To recover to the point\Nwhere I can live a normal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will take about a month, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be great if you could\Nrecover faster than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess there's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we do this together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Salome in Vegas"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything about it was fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were some people who\Nmurmured that I'd come down in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I appeared off-Broadway in\Na show that wasn't even all that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that didn't bother me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there was something\Nthere that motivated me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "This is my new stage."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Cathy is my new partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your new partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that I'll also be considered your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my dream to be able to appear\Non the same stage with you, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your dream after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, your current\Ndream will come true tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... well... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beat Sora and... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Miss Layla's current dream is here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went and brewed coffee for\Nboth of you, and you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Cathy is my new partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm no longer Miss Layla's partner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're walking down different\Npaths, so that's natural.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that, but... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never expected to hear it so clearly,\Nstraight out of Miss Layla's mouth like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never expected to feel so lonely\Njust hearing one word from Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, I can't stand on my own at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's pathetic... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is not good. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't be able to perform\Ntomorrow the way I feel now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to pull myself together. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla's constellation, Leo,\Nwhich emits a blindingly bright light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And standing motionless in\Nits shadow, Sora's Sagittarius,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's lost sight of the target\Nit should be aiming its arrows at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, don't worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just perform the way you feel like doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop looking at me with puppy eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on the stage with enough spirit\Nto steal the part of Salome from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salome, please dance for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to dance right now, Herron.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart might be the only \Nthing in this country
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn't always do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salome...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johann, your skin is as \Nwhite as new fallen snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your lips are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salome, don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johann!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johann...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get on the stage with enough spirit\Nto steal the part of Salome from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Herron, I will dance for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, I want you to grant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now the match begins, you two. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attract the audience's eyes. Upstage me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to meet Miss Layla's expectations...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do a performance\Nwhich exceeds Miss Layla's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be acknowledged. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not beaten by May. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not beaten by Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to win no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will make sure I win. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cannot beat Miss Layla. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me for anything you want, Salome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla's shining\Nsupremely on this stage too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But still... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't catch up with her at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't match Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I was able\Nto create a satisfying show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cathy understood what I meant when I said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we didn't have enough temperature on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's why you invited me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could show her what a\Nheated stage was really like if I was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I was still at Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid that you would\Novertake me from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't able to feel\Nthat edge from you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're having a hard time,\Nyou're the only person who can save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're aiming at, \Nwhat you want to grasp,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only person who knows \Nthose things is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the answers are inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My current dream is on this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the dream I told you about on that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is also my important dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my dream, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can become a true Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going after your \Ndream without being lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, I'm sure the road to\Nbeing a real Kaleido Star will open for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going after my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say hello to \Neveryone at Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes.\N{\i1}--Yes{\i0}! Don't worry. I'll take care of it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can see Fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit that I misunderstood\Nyou about Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't mean I'm\Ngiving up competing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what I want to do now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The answer is inside of me... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sekasu you ni muragaru Hard luck{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagasarete Time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yokoku doori Take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:23:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tsuredasu yo imasugu {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.83,0:23:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gouin only (saisoku drive) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nichijou miorosu best view {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asu no tame ni escape {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bakansu nashi demo oashisu wa get{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keitai off tte ai o charge shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yasashisa dake ja iyasenai itami mo aru kara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.88,0:23:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone. Surechigau{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koukai no hate ni deau true heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naite mo waratte mo I’ll be with U{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:57.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star: New Wings"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.75,0:24:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to see Dad \Nlooking sad like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, we decided to do a\NKids' Stage for the children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow, Marion is really good at the trampoline!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not doing the trampoline. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you going to bury your dream\Nalong with your mother's memories?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to bring the smile back to\NMarion's face. I want to! I want to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star,\N"Marion's Amazing Debut."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on towards the sky...{\i0}
